"Thanks to a transformative grant from Wellcome of $3.6M over three years, we're working to integrate funding metadata into OpenAlex. Our goal: to have the most comprehensive research funding database connected to other parts of the research ecosystem (institutions, authors, topics, funded outputs, etc.) openly available. Researchers, institutions, and funders will have all their funding intelligence needs met by an open system with open data. In this webinar, Kyle Demes (OpenAlex COO) will review work to date, highlight future directions, and provide more information for funders who are interested in making their metadata more available."

