"Applying the Principles of Open Science Monitoring worldwide also means localising them in many languages.

Thanks to the collaborative efforts of community members, the Italian and Portuguese (Brazil) translations of the Principles are available!&nbsp;

Read the Principles in Arabic, English, Finnish, French, German, Indonesian, Italian, Portuguese (Brazil), and Spanish:&nbsp;https://open-science-monitoring.org/principles/&nbsp;&nbsp;

Translations into Japanese, Bengali, Turkish and Slovenian are also underway."
